00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,850
Are you telling people
that you’re an alien again?

253
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:14,590
What have I told you
about playing these pranks?

254
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:17,630
i do apologize
if my boy has been a bother.

255
00:10:17,690 --> 00:10:20,660
They actually took him seriously
at his school in Tokyo.

256
00:10:20,730 --> 00:10:22,860
You should have seen
the ruckus he caused.

257
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:24,000
( Laughs )

258
00:10:24,070 --> 00:10:25,800
Now, if you’ll excuse us.

259
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:28,400
Josuke: Huh? What?

260
00:10:28,470 --> 00:10:31,170
Mikitaka: I brainwashed her.
Isn’t that great?

261
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,540
As far as she knows,
i’m her son.

262
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:37,410
Mikitaka hazekura is my alias
while i’m here on earth.

263
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,710
So long for now!

264
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:41,620
mrs. Hazekura:
Mikitaka! It’s time to go!

265
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:43,620
( Josuke gasping )

266
00:10:45,890 --> 00:10:48,160
Yoshihiro: What the hell
is going on here?

267
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:50,430
Just who the devil
was that oddball?

268
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,590
Was he serious
about being an alien,

269
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:54,930
or was he simply
a stand user I created

270
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,030
when I threw the arrow
and cut his neck?

271
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:59,170
the way that boy
was able to drive a wedge

272
00:10:59,230 --> 00:11:02,370
between josuke and Rohan was
certainly a sight to behold,

273
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,870
but he’s out.

274
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:07,640
Next they’ll face the stand,
highway go go!

275
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:09,540
it’ll crush
whoever hunts my son.

276
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,060
Josuke: Eh?

277
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,760
Rohan: Hmm?

278
00:11:27,860 --> 00:11:29,060
( Josuke gasps )

279
00:11:29,130 --> 00:11:31,100
rohan: Are you
just going to ignore me?

280
00:11:31,170 --> 00:11:34,440
The least you could do is
say hello. It’s common courtesy

281
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:38,410
to address those older
than you, josuke higashikata.

282
00:11:38,470 --> 00:11:40,680
( Josuke gasps )

283
00:11:40,740 --> 00:11:42,540
Sorry about yesterday.

284
00:11:42,610 --> 00:11:45,410
So, uh, that fire was crazy,
wasn’t it?

285
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:47,050
rohan: Yes.
That was approximately

286
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:49,550
2.5 million yen
worth of furniture.

287
00:11:49,620 --> 00:11:52,690
those pieces were
used in the movie
"pretty woman," you know?

288
00:11:52,750 --> 00:11:55,020
Not that any of that
bothers me.

289
00:11:55,090 --> 00:11:56,090
( Josuke gasps )

290
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:58,860
Rohan: What? Have a seat.

291
00:12:02,900 --> 00:12:05,030
Mark my words. I’ll repay you

292
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:07,800
for yesterday’s game
one way or another.

293
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:11,810
( Rohan gasps )

294
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:12,940
Uh...

295
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:15,640
That was...

296
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:17,150
Josuke, did you see that?

297
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:19,650
There was a door to a house
in the tunnel wall.

298
00:12:19,710 --> 00:12:22,420
- Someone’s inside.
- ( Josuke gasps )

299
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,420
( Rohan gasps )

300
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,050
It’s a window.

301
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,950
there’s a room
beyond these tunnel walls,

302
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:29,390
and, from what I can see,
someone’s living in it!

303
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:35,100
there’s a man, too,
but I can’t see their faces!

304
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:37,830
What is he attempting to do?

305
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:42,100
( Gasping )

306
00:12:45,940 --> 00:12:47,780
Josuke! Tell me you saw that!

307
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,740
Josuke: Enough!
I’ve had it with you!

308
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,880
Don’t think you can
screw with me forever!

309
00:12:51,950 --> 00:12:52,880
( Driver gasps )

310
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:57,120
Rohan: No one else
can see the room.

311
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:04,090
Is that house a new stand user?

312
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:06,030
The man who cut off
that woman’s hand,

313
00:13:06,090 --> 00:13:09,130
could he be yoshikage Kira?

314
00:13:18,610 --> 00:13:20,540
Josuke: You expect me to believe

315
00:13:20,610 --> 00:13:22,380
there was a room
inside the tunnel?!

316
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,080
You’re not fooling anyone.

317
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:27,620
is that half-baked lie
your way of getting back at me?

318
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,620
Rohan: So you have
no faith in me.

319
00:13:29,680 --> 00:13:30,950
Is that what you’re saying?

320
00:13:31,020 --> 00:13:32,820
- ( Josuke gasps )
- Rohan: That’s rich

321
00:13:32,890 --> 00:13:34,560
coming from a cheater
like you.

322
00:13:34,620 --> 00:13:36,160
And not only are you a cheater.

323
00:13:36,220 --> 00:13:38,690
You’re a cheater who lies
to cover his tracks.

324
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:41,460
You have the gall
to accuse me of lying?

325
00:13:41,530 --> 00:13:44,470
Well, I should have known
we would never see eye to eye.

326
00:13:44,530 --> 00:13:45,670
You wouldn’t understand,

327
00:13:45,730 --> 00:13:48,040
even if I took you
back there to see it.

328
00:13:51,670 --> 00:13:54,010
Right. Let’s do this.

329
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:56,510
♪

330
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,030
( Gasps )

331
00:14:14,100 --> 00:14:16,000
The exit.

332
00:14:21,770 --> 00:14:22,970
There’s nothing here.

333
00:14:23,040 --> 00:14:25,110
I could have sworn
there was something,

334
00:14:25,170 --> 00:14:26,810
but it’s just a wall.

335
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:29,540
So it was an illusion.

336
00:14:30,810 --> 00:14:32,010
Eh? What?!

337
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,820
( Groans )

338
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:35,380
( Gasps )

339
00:14:35,450 --> 00:14:37,420
Wait. This is...

340
00:14:37,490 --> 00:14:40,590
It’s the room
I saw from the bus.

341
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,930
It just appeared
out of thin air.

342
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,930
But what happened to the man
and woman who were in here?

343
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,730
- ( Rustling )
- ( Gasps )

344
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:57,070
( Thumping )

345
00:14:57,140 --> 00:14:58,640
( Rohan gasps )

346
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:00,070
♪

347
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:01,980
Blast it. Something’s in there.

348
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:04,750
This room is a trap,
and I fell for it!

349
00:15:04,810 --> 00:15:06,380
( Thumping )

350
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:08,850
Whatever’s in there’s
getting closer!

351
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:11,390
I don’t see a thing,
but something is coming!

352
00:15:11,450 --> 00:15:13,990
- ( Gasps )
- ( Engine roars )

353
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,390
That wouldn’t have ended well.

354
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:18,690
It was totally invisible,

355
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:20,830
but something
was moving toward me,

356
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:22,730
something nonhuman.

357
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,630
That room was bait,

358
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:27,740
and the Kira-looking fellow
was an illusion.

359
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:30,710
There’s no doubt in my mind
that room is a stand.

360
00:15:30,770 --> 00:15:33,140
Going it alone is risky.
I should tell Mr. Joestar.

361
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:35,940
- ( Running footsteps )
- ( Gasps )

362
00:15:36,010 --> 00:15:38,110
Damn it! It’s still coming!

363
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:42,520
What the hell?! They--

364
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:44,750
they look just like
living footprints!

365
00:15:44,820 --> 00:15:45,950
Are they the stand?

366
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:48,720
( Gasps ) How are they so fast?!

367
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:52,030
I got away.

368
00:15:52,090 --> 00:15:55,760
So it can’t run faster
than 60 kilometers per hour.

369
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:57,670
It’s a long-range stand.

370
00:15:57,730 --> 00:15:59,530
- ( Truck horn honking )
- eh?

371
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:06,010
What? It caught up to me!

372
00:16:06,070 --> 00:16:08,340
But I only lowered my speed
by a fraction.

373
00:16:09,580 --> 00:16:11,610
Aw, shit.

374
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:14,950
i’ll make it a book and
take control with heaven’s door!

375
00:16:16,050 --> 00:16:17,420
( Gags )

376
00:16:17,490 --> 00:16:21,620
No. It’s sapping my strength.

377
00:16:21,690 --> 00:16:23,620
♪

378
00:16:23,690 --> 00:16:25,860
Josuke: I was hoping
i’d never have to see

379
00:16:25,930 --> 00:16:28,630
rohan’s smug face again,
but here I am.

380
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:30,570
He may think i’m a dumb liar,

381
00:16:30,630 --> 00:16:33,000
but he’ll see
that I have a heart, too.

382
00:16:33,070 --> 00:16:34,840
Now where the heck is that guy?

383
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:40,940
What?!

384
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:43,450
( Crash )

385
00:16:43,510 --> 00:16:45,110
Is that rohan’s motorcycle?

386
00:16:45,180 --> 00:16:47,450
Why’d it just fly
out of the tunnel?

387
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:48,650
And where’s Rohan?!

388
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:51,420
( Rohan groaning )

389
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:56,460
It’s a monster.

390
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:58,730
Highway go go:
Utterly delectable.

391
00:16:58,790 --> 00:17:00,860
You shall become my nourishment!

392
00:17:00,930 --> 00:17:02,630
( Rohan groans ) Heaven’s door!

393
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:06,600
Heaven’s door: This stand’s name
is highway go go.

394
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:08,340
That room was his trap.

395
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:10,540
it hunts down
anyone who enters the room.

396
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:13,110
Then it pursues them
like a rabid dog.

397
00:17:13,170 --> 00:17:14,810
When it finally catches them,

398
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:17,010
it drains them
of all their nutrients.

399
00:17:17,080 --> 00:17:20,680
If highway go go is able
to touch you, its weakness...

400
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:22,680
Rohan: Disappears?!

401
00:17:22,750 --> 00:17:25,690
That’s crazy!

402
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:28,390
I-it’s no use.

403
00:17:28,460 --> 00:17:30,090
My strength is fading.

404
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:31,890
I can’t even read.

405
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:35,030
he’s depleting
more and more of my strength.

406
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:38,100
Writing in a command
is impossible now.

407
00:17:38,170 --> 00:17:40,900
Heaven’s door: What now?

408
00:17:40,970 --> 00:17:42,100
Josuke: Rohan!

409
00:17:42,170 --> 00:17:43,100
( Rohan gasps )

410
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,710
Josuke: Hey! Rohan, you here?!

411
00:17:45,770 --> 00:17:48,880
rohan: Josuke.
You actually came back.

412
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:51,650
highway go go:
You have a friend. How nice.

413
00:17:51,710 --> 00:17:54,120
Rohan, I believe he said.

414
00:17:54,180 --> 00:17:56,120
( Rohan gasps )

415
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:58,420
♪

416
00:17:58,490 --> 00:18:02,020
Josuke: Hey, Rohan,
answer me! Come on!

417
00:18:02,090 --> 00:18:04,090
Rohan!

418
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:05,690
( Gasps )

419
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,530
Wait. Is that...

420
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,970
What the--Rohan!

421
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:14,000
Highway go go: Well, go ahead.

422
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:16,400
Call your friend over
so he can rescue you.

423
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:17,910
Josuke: What in the world’s
going on, Rohan?

424
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:19,810
highway go go:
Shout out for help. Do it.

425
00:18:19,870 --> 00:18:21,710
There’s nothing stopping you.

426
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:24,750
i’ve left a fraction
of your body’s nutrients behind.

427
00:18:24,810 --> 00:18:27,650
If you agree to call out
for his assistance,

428
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:30,450
I might be kind enough
to spare your life.

429
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:34,120
I’ll simply go after him
instead of sucking you dry.

430
00:18:34,190 --> 00:18:37,860
Now, then, why don’t you
make this easy for everyone

431
00:18:37,930 --> 00:18:40,130
and lure him into the room?

432
00:18:40,190 --> 00:18:41,630
( Rohan panting )

433
00:18:41,700 --> 00:18:43,500
highway go go:
You want to live, don’t you?

434
00:18:43,570 --> 00:18:45,730
all you need to do
is get him to walk inside.

435
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:47,640
Josuke: What the hell
is this place?

436
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:50,510
If I didn’t know any better,
i’d say someone lives here.

437
00:18:50,570 --> 00:18:53,480
Highway go go: Hurry, and open
your mouth before it’s too late.

438
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:56,310
If you don’t act now,
he’s likely to walk away.

439
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:59,750
It’s not as if you two actually
care about each other, right?

440
00:18:59,810 --> 00:19:02,780
last chance.
Ask him to save you.

441
00:19:04,550 --> 00:19:06,050
Maybe you want to die.

442
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:07,820
Rohan: If--

443
00:19:07,890 --> 00:19:09,960
if I bait him into coming,

444
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:12,460
if I hand him over to you,

445
00:19:12,530 --> 00:19:16,970
will--will you really keep
your promise and spare my life?

446
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:19,600
I need to hear you
say the words.

447
00:19:19,670 --> 00:19:22,670
( Highway go go laughs )

448
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:24,840
But of course
I give you my word.

449
00:19:24,910 --> 00:19:27,040
If you hold up your end
of our arrangement,

450
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,580
no harm will come to you.

451
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,410
Now speak.

452
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:32,780
Bring me my meal.

453
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:34,880
Rohan: Sorry, but I refuse.

454
00:19:34,950 --> 00:19:36,580
- Highway go go: What?!
- Rohan: You should know

455
00:19:36,650 --> 00:19:39,050
that one of Rohan kishibe’s
favorite pastimes

456
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:42,060
is saying no to fools
who think they’re tough shit,

457
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:44,830
so i’m afraid
your meal’s been cancelled.

458
00:19:44,890 --> 00:19:46,730
- Josuke, run!
- ( Josuke gasps )

459
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:49,460
Rohan: No matter what happens,
you can’t come in this room!

460
00:19:49,530 --> 00:19:50,630
If you do, you’re dead!

461
00:19:50,700 --> 00:19:51,870
( Josuke gasps )

462
00:19:51,930 --> 00:19:54,000
( Highway go go groans )
you bastard!

463
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:55,070
( Rohan chuckles )

464
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:57,870
♪

465
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:00,910
josuke: You really
don’t know me at all, do you?

466
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:03,810
I’m not one to sit back
and do as i’m told.

467
00:20:03,880 --> 00:20:06,910
Now let me at this dick-wad!
His ass is grass!

468
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:10,020
Tell me where he’s hiding,
and i’ll get to work.

469
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:12,750
Rohan: What? Didn’t you
hear a single word I said?

470
00:20:12,820 --> 00:20:13,990
You have to escape!

471
00:20:14,060 --> 00:20:16,460
I just told you he’s deadly.

472
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:19,690
You always do the exact opposite
of what i’m thinking.

473
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:23,000
That’s why I despise you
with a burning passion.

474
00:20:23,060 --> 00:20:25,530
that’s why you
bug the shit out of me!

475
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,600
He’s going to attack you, fool!

476
00:20:27,670 --> 00:20:29,840
You’ve already let him
grab hold of your scent!

477
00:20:31,140 --> 00:20:32,670
( Josuke groans )

478
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:34,680
Highway go go: At last!
time to eat!

479
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:37,080
Rohan: Heaven’s door!

480
00:20:40,850 --> 00:20:42,750
( Josuke screams )

481
00:20:42,820 --> 00:20:45,750
Rohan: Josuke, highway go go
will follow you anywhere

482
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:47,990
at a speed
of 60 kilometers per hour!

483
00:20:48,060 --> 00:20:49,590
You have to find the user!

484
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:51,160
your only way
out of this predicament

485
00:20:51,230 --> 00:20:52,930
is to defeat the thing’s user!

486
00:20:52,990 --> 00:20:55,030
highway go go:
You just don’t shut up, do you?

487
00:20:55,100 --> 00:20:56,200
It’s a bad habit.

488
00:20:56,260 --> 00:21:00,370
( Josuke gasps ) Rohan!

489
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:08,140
( Groans )

490
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:10,410
I can’t believe it.

491
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:12,780
Rohan went out of his way
to save me.

492
00:21:12,850 --> 00:21:16,020
It’s weird. I’m getting
all choked up over it.

493
00:21:16,080 --> 00:21:17,750
The guy’s all right.

494
00:21:17,820 --> 00:21:19,750
♪

495
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:23,760
Leave it to me, Rohan.

496
00:21:23,830 --> 00:21:27,960
You said all I had to do
was find its user,

497
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,960
but i’ll do much more than that.

498
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:32,530
I’m gonna pummel
his soul-sucking ass.

499
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:37,640
Hang in there, Rohan!

500
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:42,040
♪

501
00:22:02,630 --> 00:22:04,070
♪ Anytime I need
to see your face ♪

502
00:22:04,130 --> 00:22:06,800
♪ I just close my eyes,
and I am taken to a place ♪

503
00:22:06,870 --> 00:22:08,770
♪ where your crystal mind
and magenta feelings ♪

504
